<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Mein willig dienst bevor. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als mir ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie meins
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>landschr<ex>eiber</ex></expan>, den ir von der hab
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gen Pfreymd geschikt hett, niht möcht
                                <expan>geschik<ex>en</ex></expan>, denn daz
                            <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Truchsess, Niclas
                                <expan>Kleissental<ex>er,</ex></expan>
                            A<expan>ndr<ex>es</ex></expan>
<expan>Prökendorff<ex>er</ex></expan> und Nikel Erhart
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, was in zu teil worden sey etc., das han ich
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und han die sache an mein
                        frewnd, den rate zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, also bracht. Die
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iren <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>kawfflewt<ex>en</ex></expan>, die die sache antrift, das also ze
                        wissen getan; die <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz sie darczu niht
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan>, es <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> denn, daz
                        sie <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stünde<ex>n,</ex></expan> was
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wievil der hab
                            <expan>vorhande<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e,</expan> die die <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>keren</expan>
<expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>; da mugt ir ewch wol nach
                                <expan>richt<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wa ich
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> die Mathei
                            <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li.</expan> Erhart Schürstab zu
                                <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>. </ab>
</div>
